OL,3,CMiddle East faces uncertainty after
OL,4,CTrump claims Ayatollah killed
OL,6,FThe Middle East faces further
OL,7,Funcertainty after Iran's Supreme
OL,8,FLeader was reportedly killed in joint
OL,9,FUS-Israeli strikes on the country.
OL,11,FUS President Donald Trump claimed
OL,12,FAyatollah Ali Khamenei had died in the
OL,13,Fattacks on Saturday morning and urged
OL,14,Fthe Iranian people to seize "the
OL,15,Fsingle greatest chance ... to take
OL,16,Fback their country".
