OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772436956
OL,3,CMiddle East faces uncertainty after
OL,4,CTrump claims Ayatollah killed
OL,6,FThe Government has not yet commented
OL,7,Fon reports of the Ayatollah's death,
OL,8,Fbut shadow foreign secretary Dame
OL,9,FPriti Patel said: "No-one should shed
OL,10,Fany tears for the death of Khamenei."
OL,12,FSaturday's attack prompted retaliation
OL,13,Ffrom Iran, with strikes reported in
OL,14,Fseveral Gulf countries including the
OL,15,FUnited Arab Emirates, Qatar, Bahrain
OL,16,Fand Saudi Arabia.
OL,26,@qD@SOUrD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
