PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772436956
OL,3,CMiddle East faces uncertainty after
OL,4,CTrump claims Ayatollah killed
OL,6,FTalks between the US and Iran aimed at
OL,7,Fresolving the issue of Tehran's
OL,8,Fnuclear ambitions ended on Thursday
OL,9,Fwithout agreement, but were expected
OL,10,Fto resume at a later date.
OL,12,FFollowing the strikes, Sir Keir
OL,13,FStarmer convened the Government's
OL,14,Femergency Cobra committee on Saturday
OL,15,Fmorning, before consulting with
OL,16,FEuropean and Gulf allies.
OL,18,FLater on Saturday, Sir Keir spoke to
OL,19,FMr Trump to discuss the situation and
OL,20,Fset out the UK's role in defensive
OL,21,Foperations in the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
